a/coordinator:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/coordinator:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/coinflip:typecheck: cache hit, replaying logs 39fc47b972a45e32\n@rng-utopia/coinflip:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/coinflip:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/coinflip@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/coinflip\n@rng-utopia/coinflip:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/coinflip:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/close-call:typecheck: cache hit, replaying logs a1031cf435ec1bf0\n@rng-utopia/close-call:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/close-call:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/close-call@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/close-call\n@rng-utopia/close-call:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/close-call:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/lord-of-rngs:typecheck: cache hit, replaying logs 6ed8c424229f1ee2\n@rng-utopia/lord-of-rngs:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/lord-of-rngs:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/lord-of-rngs@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/lord-of-rngs\n@rng-utopia/lord-of-rngs:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/lord-of-rngs:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:typecheck: cache hit, replaying logs f9185c9f9e9929a3\n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/chart-the-course@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/chart-the-course\n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/crash-simulator:typecheck: cache hit, replaying logs 5ee24332ce7a9d90\n@rng-utopia/crash-simulator:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/crash-simulator:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/crash-simulator@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/crash-simulator\n@rng-utopia/crash-simulator:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/crash-simulator:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/tug-of-earn:typecheck: cache hit, replaying logs 208534a57142d5cc\n@rng-utopia/tug-of-earn:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/tug-of-earn:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/tug-of-earn@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/tug-of-earn\n@rng-utopia/tug-of-earn:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/tug-of-earn:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/slots-utopia:typecheck: cache hit, replaying logs e2a5dd74f6c9f9be\n@rng-utopia/slots-utopia:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/platform:typecheck: cache miss, executing cec9c5ed8375bae3\n@rng-utopia/slots-utopia:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/slots-utopia@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/slots-utopia\n@rng-utopia/slots-utopia:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/slots-utopia:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/game-of-trades:typecheck: cache hit, replaying logs 7ee31b2469ae4232\n@rng-utopia/game-of-trades:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/game-of-trades:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/game-of-trades@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/game-of-trades\n@rng-utopia/game-of-trades:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/game-of-trades:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/platform:typecheck: \n@rng-utopia/platform:typecheck: > @rng-utopia/platform@0.1.0 typecheck /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform\n@rng-utopia/platform:typecheck: > tsc --noEmit\n@rng-utopia/platform:typecheck: \n\n Tasks:    17 successful, 17 total\nCached:    16 cached, 17 total\n  Time:    11.657s","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
